data.description: Country Living at it's finest! This Gorgeous property is located in West Odessa on .7 of an acre! This home boast fine craftmanship and is in impeccable condition! When you walk in you will find a spacious open floor plan that leads into a gorgeous white Kitchen with granite countertops throughout. This home has three large bedrooms with the primary having a walk in shower, you have to see for yourself!! Call your Realtor ASAP to schedule a showing!! Mobile home EXCLUDED from Sale.
